original: A BioCo Assembly Machine, capable of creating a wide range of BioCo tech.
translation: BioCo组装机，能够制造各种BioCo产物。

original: A BioCo Chemical Engine, capable of creating a wide BioCo concoction.
translation: 一个生物化学引擎，能够创造一个广泛的生物混合物。

original: A BioCo manufacturing device for various chemical components and medicines. Must be set up prior to use.
translation: 各种化学成分和药物的生物制造设备。必须在使用前设置。

original: A blue concoction of various chemicals, used by BioCo Chemical Engines.
translation: 蓝色的各种化学物质的混合物，用于生物化学发动机。

original: A bottle of pills meant for relieving nasuea and preventing vomitting.
translation: 一瓶用来缓解鼻塞和防止呕吐的药丸。

original: A broken BioCo ScavBot. Disassembly should yield a handful of useful parts.
translation: 一个坏了的BioCo ScavBot。拆卸会产生一些有用的零件。

original: A bundle of components essential in any advance crafting machine.
translation: 在任何先进的手工艺机器中必不可少的一捆部件。

original: A can full of water-soluble ETF, or Emergency Trauma Foam. When sprayed on a wound ETF rapidly expands, stopping bleeding, acting as a local painkiller, and also disinfecting the wound.
translation: 装满水溶性ETF或急救泡沫的罐子。当喷在伤口上时，ETF会迅速扩张，止血，起到局部止痛药的作用，同时还能对伤口进行消毒。

original: A collection of top quality machine to human interfaces, advance semiconductors, and other important components to BioCo tech. Useful in both bionics and advance electronics.
translation: 高质量的人机界面，先进的半导体，以及生物技术的其他重要组件的集合。在仿生学和先进的电子技术中都有用。

original: A dense and oddly non-technical binder full of detailed descriptions of various chemical processes used by the BioCo Chemical Engine. While a lot of these are beyond you, there's a few you think you might be able to replicate.
translation: 一种密度大、奇怪的非技术性的粘合剂，里面详细描述了生物化学引擎使用的各种化学过程。虽然这些都超出了你的能力范围，但有一些你认为你可以复制。

original: A large processing unit on an electric board. An essential component to BioCo machines.
translation: 电路板上的一种大型处理单元。是BioCo机器的重要组成部分。

original: A set of comprehensive blueprints loaded onto a USB which detail the AutoDocs created by BioCo. While gibberish to you, one of BioCo's assembly machines could read this.
translation: 加载到USB上的一套全面的蓝图，详细说明了由BioCo创建的AutoDocs。当你胡言乱语的时候，BioCo的一台组装机能读懂这个。

original: A set of comprehensive blueprints loaded onto a USB which detail the Military CBMs created by BioCo. While gibberish to you, one of BioCo's assembly machines could read this.
translation: 加载到USB上的一套全面的蓝图，详细说明了BioCo创建的军事CBM。当你胡言乱语的时候，BioCo的一台组装机能读懂这个。

original: A set of comprehensive blueprints loaded onto a USB which detail the medical CBMs created by BioCo. While gibberish to you, one of BioCo's assembly machines could read this.

original: A set of comprehensive blueprints loaded onto a USB which detail the medical supplies created by BioCo. While gibberish to you, one of BioCo's Chemical Engines could read this.

original: A set of comprehensive blueprints loaded onto a USB which detail the power storage CBMs created by BioCo. While gibberish to you, one of BioCo's assembly machines could read this.

original: A significantly less than portable assembly of autonomous surgeon machines used for the installation of bionics. Must be set up prior to use.
translation: 用于安装仿生学的自主外科医生机器的一种明显不便于携带的组件。必须在使用前设置。

original: A significantly less than portable couch loaded with sensors of all varieties, for use next to a BioCo AutoDoc unit. Must be set up prior to use.
translation: 一种比便携式沙发小得多的沙发，装有各种各样的传感器，用于BioCo AutoDoc装置旁边。必须在使用前设置。

original: A slightly shimmering green concoction of various chemicals, used by BioCo Chemical Engines.
translation: 一种微亮的绿色混合物，由各种化学物质混合而成，用于生物化学发动机。

original: A small, retractable launcher resides in the palm of your hand through your arm. The system will automatically produce small gelatinous orbs that when launched into fire will rapidly expand into a fire fighting foam.
translation: 一个小型的，可伸缩的发射器安置在你的手臂和手掌中。这个系统将自动产生小的凝胶状球体，当它被射入火中时会迅速膨胀成灭火泡沫。

original: A small, retractable launcher resides in the palm of your hand through your arm. The system will automatically produce small gelatinous orbs that when launched into fire will rapidly expand into a fire fighting foam.

translation: 用于安装和卸载仿生学的外科器械。它的技术和它的操作员一样熟练。

original: A thick slurry of calories and nutrients. Suprisingly tasty!
translation: 热量和营养的浓浆。美味无比！

translation: 一种很薄的紫色混合物，由各种化学物质混合而成，用于生物化学发动机。

original: Adds many new bionic centric items, courtesy of BioCo
translation: 添加了许多新的仿生中心项目，由BioCo提供

translation: 这个膝盖高的蜘蛛机器人用多条腿蹦蹦来蹦去，它的顶部有BioCo标志。
